14 October 1980
The First Public Programme In Germany
Public Program
Freiburg (Germany)
Talk Language: English | Transcript (English) - NOT needed

*“The first public programme in Germany was on 14.10. 1980. I rented the Freiburg college lecture hall and was nervous, knowing I might have to speak. Shri Mataji arrived with Gregoire’s wife Catherine and five yogis. The programme was well attended. Thomas Menge.”

